      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable mode of transportation who isn't concerned with perfection. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though it could benefit from a tune-up and some routine maintenance to improve overall smoothness. The transmission shifts through all gears, but the shift quality is not as crisp as a newer model. On the exterior, you will find several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and clear coat fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few stains, though it remains functional. All major electronics like the lights and wipers work, but the air conditioning is not blowing as cold as it used to. This is a solid, honest car that will get you from A to B with some character.",
