      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are operational, though you may notice some typical signs of age such as minor fluid seeps and a less-than-perfect idle. The exterior has its share of scratches, small dents, and some paint fading, while the interior shows clear signs of use including worn upholstery and some loose trim pieces. It's a solid, no-frills car that will get you from point A to point B reliably, provided you keep up with basic maintenance.",
